text: Itumbiara explanata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1885, originally under the genus Isomerida. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Itumbiara explanata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1885
